		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">jogynes wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I tried to modify the source code to have no damage. i find in enemy.s the increment damage counter</div><br />You want <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">HurtPlayer</tt> in <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">global.s</tt>. You can just replace its code with an RTS. What you found was code for an enemy that takes 3 shots to die.

		

		</td>
