		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Here it is, a ROM with all 33 levels and all 7 bosses, ready for playtesting purposes.<br /><br />This ROM is <strong>not</strong> final and has some known problems that need addressing, and some other polish that I need to add (like there's still no music!), and while it's not ready for full attention from everyone and streaming (especially not reviewing), all of the gameplay should be done and ready for comments.<br /><br />I still plan to make a few more levels for epilogue purposes, and maybe throw in some more extras.

		
